917
00:41:51,620 --> 00:41:52,820
She takes better care of me.

918
00:41:54,180 --> 00:41:55,900
Does she like you?

919
00:41:56,500 --> 00:41:56,900
Her?

920
00:41:58,580 --> 00:42:00,020
She's like a tomboy.

921
00:42:00,740 --> 00:42:01,940
She probably sees me as a buddy.

922
00:42:09,044 --> 00:42:10,740
Judging the way this place is decorated,

923
00:42:10,822 --> 00:42:12,640
I'd say there's not much
of a woman's touch.

924
00:42:14,500 --> 00:42:16,700
It's just personal taste.

925
00:42:19,066 --> 00:42:20,488
Here. Take your medicine.

926
00:42:21,220 --> 00:42:21,700
Okay.

927
00:42:33,060 --> 00:42:33,940
Can you

928
00:42:34,060 --> 00:42:35,260
